{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124455850119794688538724.jpeg/c6EeVb9q3e6KvhN_Wkz16ZdMnozoaBl1tDqi_7Q6ov8\" alt=\"邵初與伍韻婷拍攝內衣廣告。（IG@kristyshaw.c）\"><figcaption>邵初與伍韻婷拍攝內衣廣告。（IG@kristyshaw.c）</figcaption></figure><p>性感大解放</p><p>原來邵初與另一TVB小花伍韻婷拍攝內衣廣告更在床上展開枕頭大戰，廣告中她們均穿上白色和碎花內衣，純潔而又有女人味，性感但不色情。不少網民也大讚：「靚到不得了呀」、「好美，又健康」。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124455852590370816564093.jpeg/malSVjcxQcuzWsfeXUdqPN_PcsLYDAJ7dy1Y0nctWNI\" alt=\"邵初好靚呀！（IG@kristyshaw.c）\"><figcaption>邵初好靚呀！（IG@kristyshaw.c）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124455854977060864570613.jpeg/dBTnM5yx4K1tGVO9ENCSDhFSl2MvfIr39CLzQ_Qi80M\" alt=\"邵初好靚呀！（IG@kristyshaw.c）\"><figcaption>邵初好靚呀！（IG@kristyshaw.c）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124455857183395840873510.jpeg/AAXTtG-Qbf4gDtSih6AJQpNWzLtmngol8M-3Q_DPt0M\" alt=\"邵初大騷健美身材。（IG@kristyshaw.c）\"><figcaption>邵初大騷健美身材。（IG@kristyshaw.c）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124455859469422592815940.jpeg/w4brYCrWhu0Xwx0GcuCEcDRz8z2xS9rSDaPCLw2jwi8\" alt=\"邵初大騷健美身材。（IG@kristyshaw.c）\"><figcaption>邵初大騷健美身材。（IG@kristyshaw.c）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124455850178514944217308.jpeg/zkziA--nup7Xnmy3UTgcBlJ4ZOU_LcyqMmw7jzJsO48\" alt=\"邵初拍攝內衣廣告。（IG@kristyshaw.c）\"><figcaption>邵初拍攝內衣廣告。（IG@kristyshaw.c）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124455852577787904519738.jpeg/B_qTs2qx1RDcrORLteZ55Y4RA0DUeHNALDXhxSw14cU\" alt=\"邵初與伍韻婷拍攝內衣廣告。（IG@kristyshaw.c）\"><figcaption>邵初與伍韻婷拍攝內衣廣告。（IG@kristyshaw.c）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124455855266467840109254.jpeg/n2FsNJJdX4yXep5vDG92F8x4bMHCQtmQ9bT2EPW09hA\" alt=\"好靚呀！（IG@kristyshaw.c）\"><figcaption>好靚呀！（IG@kristyshaw.c）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-24T16:02:26.740947+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":309,"images":8,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}